&lt;p&gt;My personal vim config&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;basic-tenants&quot;&gt;Basic tenants&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;All keybindings are in config/keybindings.vim&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Each plugin has it’s own config.vim file&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;quick-start&quot;&gt;Quick Start&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;git clone git@github.com:mikeendo/dotvim.git ~/.vim
git clone https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim
ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc.vim ~/.vimrc
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;# Vim command
:PluginInstall
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
